<tr valign="top" height="400" >
<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style=""><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>You elected to pay for your Kingsbridge business insurance policy&nbsp;<b>{!Policy__c.Name}&nbsp;</b>through direct debit payments.&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>Our credit providers Close Brothers Premium Finance require some additional information from you in order to continue providing the loan for your insurance policy.&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>You have not yet provided this information and so Close Brothers have cancelled your loan and your future payments remain outstanding. Because of this&nbsp;<b>your insurance policy is scheduled to be cancelled on&nbsp;<i>[ddmmyy]</i></b>.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>If your insurance policy is cancelled,&nbsp;<u>your business may not be covered against claims if you don't have another policy in place.&nbsp;</u><br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>To stay protected, please provide us with the requested information and call us on&nbsp;<b>01242 808740</b>&nbsp;to make a payment or discuss further.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br><u>Please note, for data security reasons, do not send credit or debit card details to us via email.</u><br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br><i>If you have made a payment in the past 3 working days please disregard this email.</i><br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>Kind regards,<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>{!User.FirstName}<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Customer Service Team<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>E:&nbsp;</span><a href="mailto:customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk" style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk</a><br style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">T: 01242 808 740</span></p>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>